 Galvatron woke up. Fully energized he hovered over the ground with great 
power. Optimus was a fool. He was no longer after hot rod........he had other 
prey in mind.  Galvatron with his new look walked into the confrence room. He 
sent a comm to Magma, "I have returned and am more powerful then ever. I wish 
to have or attack soo to test my new powers."
